<br>
Basically, you load up your inventory with the items you want to sell, put a price against each one, switch yourself into merchant mode, and log off.<br>
<br>
The game turns you into an NPC merchant, and anyone can come along and buy your items off you. When you log back in you are minus any items that were bought, and plus the cash.<br>
<br>
Interesting idea, I hope they implement it well.<br>
